34:02.102 --> 34:04.939
“To the Governing Body
and the Bethel family.


34:04.938 --> 34:07.231
“Dear Brothers:


34:07.232 --> 34:10.527
“From the moment
we received our invitations to Gilead


34:10.527 --> 34:13.114
“down to this day of graduation,


34:13.113 --> 34:18.118
“we feel we have received a gift
of undeserved kindness


34:18.118 --> 34:20.995
“from Jehovah and his organization.


34:20.995 --> 34:25.375
“There is nothing that we have done
or could ever do


34:25.375 --> 34:30.380
“to deserve the instruction,
training, molding,


34:30.380 --> 34:35.385
“and loving attention that we have
received over the past five months.


34:35.385 --> 34:40.140
“Just as Isaiah 26:12 says:


34:40.140 --> 34:42.392
“‘O Jehovah, . . .


34:42.392 --> 34:48.899
“everything we have done
you have accomplished for us.’


34:48.898 --> 34:51.443
“Jehovah has given us the privilege


34:51.443 --> 34:54.988
“of experiencing close association


34:54.988 --> 34:58.908
“with you dear brothers
of the Governing Body.


34:58.908 --> 35:03.538
“Your humility,
your love for the brotherhood,


35:03.538 --> 35:05.998
“and your absolute determination


35:05.998 --> 35:11.003
“to follow Jehovah’s direction
have deeply impressed us.


35:11.003 --> 35:16.008
“We saw this clearly
during your faith-strengthening lectures


35:16.008 --> 35:18.261
“but also in the lighter moments


35:18.262 --> 35:21.139
“that you shared with us
outside of the classroom,


35:21.138 --> 35:25.435
“all the while preparing
for your move to Warwick.


35:25.435 --> 35:30.357
“Seeing your examples firsthand
has only made us more convinced


35:30.357 --> 35:32.400
“that this is the organization


35:32.400 --> 35:37.030
“Jehovah is blessing
and directing today.


35:37.030 --> 35:40.575
“What a true joy
it has been for us


35:40.575 --> 35:45.205
“to be part of this
delightful Bethel family!


35:45.205 --> 35:49.167
“You’ve been an example
in hospitality,


35:49.167 --> 35:53.672
“making us feel at home
away from home.


35:53.672 --> 35:58.677
“The excellent work of so many departments
has created an environment


35:58.677 --> 36:01.597
“where studying day and night
and night and day


36:01.597 --> 36:05.475
“was both possible and enjoyable.


36:05.475 --> 36:09.062
“An essential part of our learning experience


36:09.062 --> 36:11.064
“has been seeing the faith


36:11.063 --> 36:15.776
“of so many of you
long-time members of the family.


36:15.777 --> 36:18.239
“We have also learned
from the faith of you,


36:18.238 --> 36:21.825
“the many commuters
and temporary volunteers,


36:21.825 --> 36:24.493
“who willingly make yourselves available


36:24.493 --> 36:27.000
“to serve here at Bethel.


36:28.540 --> 36:33.545
“We are truly grateful to you,
our dear instructors,


36:33.545 --> 36:37.090
“for generously giving of your very selves,


36:37.090 --> 36:39.508
“both mind and heart,


36:39.508 --> 36:42.053
“in the way that you have taught us.


36:42.053 --> 36:45.098
“During our training,
your love for the Bible truth


36:45.098 --> 36:47.683
“that you were teaching
touched us deeply.


36:47.683 --> 36:51.270
“Your accuracy
and yet your warmth,


36:51.270 --> 36:55.150
“your seriousness
and yet your humor


36:55.150 --> 36:59.362
“showed us a balance
worthy of imitation.


36:59.362 --> 37:03.742
“Your obvious determination
to hold fast to the direction


37:03.742 --> 37:05.869
“of ‘the faithful and discreet slave’


37:05.868 --> 37:09.371
“has made 
a lasting impression on us.


37:09.372 --> 37:13.919
“As we go to our assignments,
we are resolved to do


37:13.918 --> 37:17.838
“as 1 Peter 4:10 states:


37:17.838 --> 37:22.843
“‘To the extent that each one
has received a gift,


37:22.843 --> 37:26.681
“‘use it in ministering to one another


37:26.682 --> 37:30.185
“as fine stewards
of God’s undeserved kindness.’


37:30.185 --> 37:33.605
“Gilead has been a priceless gift


37:33.605 --> 37:36.817
“from Jehovah through all of you.


37:36.817 --> 37:40.154
“Having been shown
such undeserved kindness,


37:40.153 --> 37:46.158
“we desire to use it to demonstrate
our love for Jehovah.


37:46.158 --> 37:50.038
“More than ever before,
we are determined to continue


37:50.038 --> 37:54.876
“to advance the preaching of the good news
and to strengthen our brothers.


37:54.877 --> 38:00.715
“It is our earnest prayer
that this be our life’s work,


38:00.715 --> 38:05.553
“all to the honor and glory
of our heavenly Father, Jehovah.


38:05.553 --> 38:10.000
Your brothers and sisters
of the 141st class of Gilead.”


