39:58.542 --> 40:00.544
But “See—The Cloud!”


40:00.543 --> 40:05.340
Follow the cloud, not men—
nice reminder.


40:05.340 --> 40:08.677
And of course,
you’ll always remember Brother Herd’s talk,


40:08.677 --> 40:13.222
and nice thought, “Smells ring bells.”


40:13.222 --> 40:17.019
Again, the translators
will have fun with that.


40:17.018 --> 40:21.438
And then the warning about ego;
it’s a good caution, counsel.


40:21.438 --> 40:25.776
And nice thoughts
about testing Jehovah and being tested.


40:25.777 --> 40:29.614
And, of course, all the good experiences
and interviews


40:29.613 --> 40:34.118
and Brother Lösch reminding us
to make good use of our time.


40:34.118 --> 40:36.120
So it’s been a wonderful program.


40:36.120 --> 40:40.417
What’s nice, too,
because you get into your assignment


40:40.417 --> 40:45.380
